OL,3,CSalman Rushdie reveals 'unfair' cancer
OL,4,Cscare after knife attack
OL,6,FThe 76-year-old Indian-born British
OL,7,Fauthor suffered severe, life-changing
OL,8,Finjuries including losing sight in one
OL,9,Feye following the violent knife attack
OL,10,Fwhich occurred ahead of him delivering
OL,11,Fa lecture at the Chautauqua
OL,12,FInstitution in August 2022.
OL,14,FIn his new book, Knife: Meditations
OL,15,FAfter An Attempted Murder, Sir Salman
OL,16,Fhas recounted his experience of the
OL,17,Fnear-fatal incident and the aftermath.
