OL,3,CSalman Rushdie reveals 'unfair' cancer
OL,4,Cscare after knife attack
OL,6,FAfter recalling the event and his
OL,7,Finitial recovery process, the Booker
OL,8,FPrize-winning author explained a
OL,9,F"small bump" was found when he had his
OL,10,Fprostate examined by his doctor as
OL,11,Fpart of a health check-up.
OL,13,F"After I narrowly survived a murder
OL,14,Fattempt, now I had to face the
OL,15,Fprospect of cancer?" he wrote.
OL,17,F"This was unacceptable. It was unfair."
OL,19,FAfter undergoing an MRI scan, he
OL,20,Freceived the results which stated:
OL,21,F"Cancer likely".
