OL,6,F"The second MRI took place in
OL,7,FDecember, five weeks after Dr U-2's
OL,8,Finspection, two months after the
OL,9,Fmessage reading cancer likely. This
OL,10,Ftime the scan was clear," he wrote.
OL,12,F"On the scale of 1 to 5, I was now a
OL,13,Fproud 1. There was no lump. I didn't
OL,14,Fhave prostate cancer.
OL,16,F"The universe wasn't quite as cruel as
OL,17,Fthat, even though it had waited two
OL,18,Flong months to tell me so."
