OL,6,FWhen the attack happened on stage in
OL,7,FAugust 2022, the author was due to
OL,8,Fspeak about safe places for writers at
OL,9,Fthe event being held in the small town
OL,10,Fof Chautauqua.
OL,12,FThe incident was not the first time
OL,13,FSir Salman's life has come under
OL,14,Fthreat as in 1989 Iran's former ruler
OL,15,FAyatollah Khomeini called for his
OL,16,Fdeath after the publication of his
OL,17,Fnovel The Satanic Verses, which some
OL,18,FMuslims consider blasphemous.
OL,20,FThe Iranian government withdrew
OL,21,Fsupport for the death sentence in 1998.
