OL,6,FAhead of his new book's publication,
OL,7,FSir Salman revealed he did not want to
OL,8,Fattend the talk where he was attacked
OL,9,Fin 2022 after having a premonition of
OL,10,Fthe incident.
OL,12,FIn his first major television
OL,13,Finterview since the attack, the author
OL,14,Ftold Anderson Cooper on CBS programme
OL,15,F60 Minutes that he had dreamed of a
OL,16,Fman bearing down on him with a spear
OL,17,Fin an "amphitheatre" in the days
OL,18,Fbefore the event.
