OL,6,FThe author also explained that he does
OL,7,Fnot name his attacker ` a 24-year-old
OL,8,Fman from New Jersey named Hadi Matar,
OL,9,Fwho has pleaded not guilty and is
OL,10,Fawaiting trial ` in the book.
OL,12,F"I don't want his name in my book and
OL,13,FI don't want him in my life," he said.
OL,15,F"We had 27 seconds together (the
OL,16,Flength of the attack), I don't want to
OL,17,Fgive him any more of my time."
